  <!-- @import "site-sidebar.kit" -->

  <p>The off-canvas sidebar is a modification to the grid system.</p>
  
  <p>Instead of setting the <code>col-[size]--span-*</code> of a sidebar col on any screen size, use the class <code>col-[size]--off-canvas</code>. You can also specify whether the behavior is  to the left or right.</p>
  
  <p>You will also need to add a navicon/toggle.</p>
  
  <p><i>Example: see the sidebar on this page at different screen widths.</i></p>

